  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0bca\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bca\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b8e\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8 \u0bae\u0bc0\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b85\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0ba4\u0bc1 - \u0b9a\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0bb0 \u0b85\u0bae\u0bc8\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bc1 \u0b8e\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The number of Covid-19 cases is increasing again - Ministry of Health warns",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Ministry of Health has reported that there has been a significant increase in the number of Covid patients in Sri Lanka.",
        "According to the Ministry of Health's Department of Infectious Diseases, 62 Covid-19 cases have been identified nationwide as of Monday.",
        "The number of Covid-19 patients has increased significantly in the last two weeks, Chief Epidemiologist of the Department of Infectious Diseases Samitha Kinike has warned.",
        "He added that research data has shown that people who have received the vaccine are better protected against the virus than those who have not received the Covid vaccine.",
        "The Public Health Inspectors Association has stated that although a significant number of Covid-infected people are being identified, there are no Covid tests in many areas like before.",
        "Therefore, the actual number of Covid-19 infections in the country may be significantly higher than the number reported by the Ministry of Health, the Association of Public Health Examiners further said."
      ],
